
  Chikorita    Grass Type Pokémon

  A sweet aroma gently wafts from 
  the leaf on its head.  It is 
  docile and loves to soak up the 
  sun's rays. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Chikorita ► Bayleef ► Meganium

